  "title": "Urgent!! Quantity Surveyor (Construction / MNC)",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Description</strong></p><ul><li><p>Prepare quotations, cost estimates, and bills of quantities (BOQ).</p></li><li><p>Source and procure required materials; negotiate with suppliers and subcontractors.</p></li><li><p>Submit work approvals to relevant local authorities.</p></li><li><p>Manage end-to-end tender administration.</p></li><li><p>Evaluate price comparisons and prepare costing summaries.</p></li><li><p>Prepare monthly progress claims for customers.</p></li><li><p>Prepare, verify, and maintain project variation works and site instructions.</p></li><li><p>Handle other quantity surveying duties as assigned.</p></li><li><p>Attend site meetings</p></li></ul><p><strong>Requirements</strong></p><ul><li><p>Degree/Diploma in relevant field of study</p></li><li><p>AutoCAD skills</p></li></ul><p><strong>HOW TO APPLY:</strong></p><p>Interested applicants, please click on <strong>“Apply Now”</strong> or submit your resume to <a href=\"mailto:ref71@trustrecruit.com.sg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><strong>ref71@trustrecruit.com.sg</strong></a></p><p>We regret only shortlisted candidates will be notified.</p><p>Important Note: Trust Recruit Pte Ltd is committed to safeguarding your personal data in accordance with the Personal Data Protection Act (PDPA).</p><p>Please read our privacy statement on our corporate website www.trustrecruit.com.sg.</p><p>Trust Recruit Pte Ltd</p><p>EA License No: 19C9950</p><p>EA Personnel: Lee Jia Xiang</p><p>EA Personnel Reg No: R25158171</p>",
